positions
Search & Apply








Our team members love working here... and it shows





                                It's exciting
and I still love coming into work
every day.
                            

                                                                        - Lauren, General Manager                                





                                Don't be afraid to
start at the ground level and learn
everything you can.
                            

                                                                        - Emily, Team Member To Marketing Manager                                





                                Noodles & Co. Provides Us
with a unique opportunity to
impact people's lives every day.
                            

                                                                        - Jared, Team Member To General Manager                                






 

Fast Track Your Future - It's Time to Start Your Road Trip
If you’re motivated, we’re behind you all the way. We always look to mentor, train and develop Noodles team members for their next opportunity. We encourage and support your growth and development and will help to build both your leadership and technical skills to help you take the next step in your Noodles career. We’ve built a company on that premise—and redefined restaurant dining in the process. We look forward to helping you become the person you’re destined to be as you create your road trip to success as a Noodler.


See the perks































Noodles & Company Catering - Pastas, Salads, & More





































Skip to main content







Catering


Everything You Need For Any Size Group

Noodles & Company brings a world of flavors under one roof—yours! And with the global variety, everyone can find something they like. We’ll help you bring the REAL Food, REAL Cooking and REAL Flavors of Noodles to your next social gathering.
Pricing varies by location.
View our Catering Nutritional Information.
 = Spicy = Vegetarian: excludes meat and fish.





Big Pans
Catering Packages



Big Pans



Big pans of fan favorites.
Each pan feeds 6-8 people and comes with plates, forks, knives, serving utensils and napkins.





