Pad Thai - Noodles.com






































Skip to main content







Pad Thai








Description
Nutrition






Rice noodle stir-fry with scrambled egg, napa and red cabbage, citrus, peanuts, Asian sprouts, green onions and cilantro.

Try with sautéed shrimp - Add 110 Cal




Dish Profile

                                                                            Dairy-free,                                                                             Sweet,                                                                             Tangy,                                                                             Traditional                                                                    

Regular: 1330 Calories
Small: 660 Calories



Nutrition & Allergen Guide



Levels of Spiciness = Spicy
 = Vegetarian: excludes meat and fish.


2,000 calories a day is used for general nutrition advice, but calorie needs vary. Additional nutrition information available upon request.







					Regular Size | 					Small Size			



Calories

													1330 | 													660											


Calories from fat

													680 | 													340											


Total fat

													75g | 													38g											


Saturated fat

															13g | 															6g													


Trans fat

															0g | 															0g													


Cholesterol

													340mg | 													170mg											


Sodium

											1300mg | 											650mg									


Total Carbohydrates

													139g | 													70g											


Dietary Fiber

													4g | 													2g											


Sugars

													30g | 													15g											


Protein

													19g | 													10g											



Dish pictured is regular size.
 






Tips to Perfection



Off the Dairy Farm
This dish is dairy-free as-is, so just order away.


Gluten Be Gone
This dish is gluten free as is.





Tasty Additions



                                Sautéed Shrimp - Add 110 Cal
                            

                                Seasoned Tofu - Add 180 Cal
                            

                                Grilled Chicken Breast - Add 90 Cal
                            




