        12/2/2016
    








1 check-in
        







First to Review
        


Noodles, noodles, & more noodles!If you and your friends are in the mood for noodles but not sure specifically what type, this is the spot. This was my first time to a Noodles & Company and I really liked the variety. From Penne Rosa (tomato-based cream sauce) to Pad Thai to Steak Stroganoff, there is something on the menu for anyone's taste. During my first visit, I tried the Penne Rosa with Parmesan-crusted Chicken Breast per staff recommendation. It was prepared in under 5 minutes. Almost took me longer to go fill my cup up with Root Beer. The food was tasty and filled me up perfectly before returning back to work. If I'm in the mood for noodles, but unsure what type initially...I'll stop back at Noodles & Company.








Penne Rosa with Parmesan-Crusted Chicken Breast


Penne Rosa with Parmesan-Crusted Chicken Breast








